Review Text: The staff is polite but a bit misleading. One salesman told me my size (34) wasn't available on sale, so I had to pick a pair at full price (5,200). Later, another salesman said the same jeans(510 Skinny Jeans)  in a lighter color were on sale for 2,900*, so I bought those instead. They still tried to push the full-price pair on me.
